---
import SectionHeader from '../ui/SectionHeader.astro';
---

<section class="py-20 lg:py-24 bg-white border-b border-brand-border/40">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <SectionHeader
      title="Who We Help"
    />

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-brand-border/60">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">Creators and Coaches</h3>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-accent mb-4">The Challenge: Too much knowledge, not enough structure.</p>
        <p class="text-brand-textMain text-sm mb-4">We help organize frameworks and coaching methodologies into structured, sellable digital courses and memberships.</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-primary border-t border-brand-border/60 pt-4 mt-auto">Outcome: A clear, launch-ready course product.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-brand-border/60">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">Consultants</h3>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-accent mb-4">The Challenge: Trading time for money.</p>
        <p class="text-brand-textMain text-sm mb-4">We help productize consulting frameworks into scalable learning assets, toolkits, and hybrid learning programs.</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-primary border-t border-brand-border/60 pt-4 mt-auto">Outcome: Scalable revenue beyond 1:1 client work.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-brand-border/60">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">Educators</h3>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-accent mb-4">The Challenge: Moving from classroom to online.</p>
        <p class="text-brand-textMain text-sm mb-4">We translate traditional lesson plans and offline curriculum into engaging, self-paced online learning experiences.</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-primary border-t border-brand-border/60 pt-4 mt-auto">Outcome: Professional digital curriculum delivery.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-brand-border/60">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">Training Companies</h3>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-accent mb-4">The Challenge: Managing messy, outdated LMS systems.</p>
        <p class="text-brand-textMain text-sm mb-4">We migrate, structure, and modernize existing training catalogs onto modern platforms like Kajabi or dedicated LMS tools.</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-primary border-t border-brand-border/60 pt-4 mt-auto">Outcome: Streamlined, modern training delivery.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-brand-border/60">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">Online Academies</h3>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-accent mb-4">The Challenge: Poor learner retention and UX.</p>
        <p class="text-brand-textMain text-sm mb-4">We improve platform architecture, student onboarding, gamification, and ongoing engagement systems.</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-primary border-t border-brand-border/60 pt-4 mt-auto">Outcome: Higher completion rates and better reviews.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-brand-border/60">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">Businesses & Teams</h3>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-accent mb-4">The Challenge: Scattered internal SOPs and training.</p>
        <p class="text-brand-textMain text-sm mb-4">We convert Google Drive folders, manuals, and loose videos into structured onboarding and internal training hubs.</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-primary border-t border-brand-border/60 pt-4 mt-auto">Outcome: Faster employee onboarding and compliance.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
